[1] Ebola outbreak update
[A] BNO News
Date: Fri 14 Oct 2022
Source: Twitter, BNO News [edited]
https://mobile.twitter.com/BNOFeed


We are still doing daily updates on Ebola when possible, but the Ugandan government has severely limited the release of information, going from daily to only sporadic updates

New cases: 4 confirmed
New deaths: 0
In hospital: 10 (-4)
Total cases: 78 (58 conf.)
Total deaths: 39 (19 conf.)
Total recovered: 23 (+3)
Case fatality rate: 63%

