[B] Helen Branswell tweet
Date: Sat 15 Oct 2022
Source: Twitter, Helen Branswell [edited]
https://twitter.com/HelenBranswell/status/


On [13 Oct 2022] there were 4 new #Ebola cases reported, all from Mubende, the most affected district. 3 of the 4 cases were known contacts of a case who were being monitored. That means 1of the 4 is someone who the contact tracers didn't know about. That is dangerous.

The #Ebola response reports that some communities are still not cooperating & that response staff are facing hostility in some places. And apparently, some of the village health teams do not believe in Ebola. (This information comes from a government situation report.)

